<li><a href="/wiki/Richard_S._Westfall" title="Richard S. Westfall">Richard S. Westfall</a>, "Short-Writing and the State of Newton's Conscience, 1662", <i>Notes and Records of the Royal Society</i> <b>18</b> (1963), 10-16.</li>
<li>Pitmans College (1975). <i>Shorthand</i>. Hodder and Stoughton. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0340056878" class="internal">ISBN 0-340-05687-8</a></li>
