<li>In Bram Stoker's <i><a href="/wiki/Dracula" title="Dracula">Dracula</a></i>, <a href="/wiki/Johnathan_Harker" title="Johnathan Harker" class="mw-redirect">Johnathan Harker's</a> journal(in the story) is written entirely in shorthand.</li>
</ul>
